&lt;p>Replace text in the current line:&lt;/p>



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="f1e880c" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>:s/original/destination/g&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;p>Replace text in the entire document:&lt;/p>



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="5284345" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>:%s/original/destination/g&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;p>Remove trailing spaces and tabs at the end of lines:&lt;/p>



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="b42663a" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>:%s/\s\&amp;#43;$//&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
